rows.label: tev068301_SEL2041
rows.name: Ask Zo Zazhi about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0001
rows.name:
They have installed themselves inside a grotesque castle
in Cauldros. ...Pah. Their evil knows no bounds.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0002
rows.name: I know you have a quarrel with them, but so do I![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0003
rows.name:
I must train hard and become stronger than anyone so
I can wring the life out of those fiends with my own
two hands![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0004
rows.name:
Consider it a challenge. Will BLADE strike them first,
or will I?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0009
rows.name:
Zo Langra says he is concerned for me,
but he can save his whimpering protests.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0010
rows.name:
I am a warrior, not some precious maiden!
I intend to take up arms and visit every indignity we
have suffered back upon our enemies tenfold![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0011
rows.name:
Know thisâ€”my elder brothers taught me well,
and I will prove it by besting you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0012
rows.name:
Then I will seek out my hated enemy, wring the life
from him, and exact vengeance for my brothers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0017
rows.name:
I tried to join you on the front lines during the
mission to the Lifehold Core. How I tried![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0018
rows.name:
But Zo Langra, my fool of a little brother, interfered.
He told me I would have to cut him down before he
would let me leave.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0019
rows.name: And now I missed the final battle... How it vexes me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG0020
rows.name:
I wanted to be the first to drive my sword into
Luxaar's cold, black heart![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG1001
rows.name: He is dead? I see. Then maybe...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG1002
rows.name:
Thank you, [ST:playername ].
Maybe now my elder brothers can rest in peace.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG1003
rows.name:
From now on, I shall fulfill my duty as heiress to the
House of Zo and act responsibly. Langra and I will
ensure our house survives and flourishes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG1004
rows.name:
And if any dare attempt to tarnish our honor,
I will make them pay dearly...or die trying.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2001
rows.name: Besides my elder brothers, there is another I admire.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2002
rows.name:
Her name is Ge Jewhe, and she is just
the sort of woman and warrior I strive to be.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2003
rows.name:
I feared for her when I heard she ran off to exact
justice upon the Ganglion, but to my delight,
she has returned home safely.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2004
rows.name:
...Ah. I see now. This is how my little brother must
have felt when I came home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2005
rows.name: Again, Ge Jewhe teaches me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2010
rows.name: Besides my elder brothers, there was another I admired.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2011
rows.name:
Her name was Ge Jewhe, and she was just the sort of
woman and warrior I strive to be.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2012
rows.name:
I feared for her when I heard she ran off to exact
justice upon the Ganglion, and was greatly dismayed
at the news of her death.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2013
rows.name: Twice now, I have felt the pain of being left behind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev068301_MSG2014
rows.name:
Now I must do my part to stop any more of my
friends from dying. Ge Jewhe's death must not
be in vain![ST:wait ]
